<article id="post-14602" class="post-14602 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-agile category-productivity tag-agile tag-coach tag-coaching tag-productivity-2">
	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.garethjmsaunders.co.uk/2025/11/20/a-new-chapter-opening-my-productivity-and-agile-coaching-programme/" rel="bookmark">A new chapter: opening my productivity and agile coaching programme</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="750" height="500" src="https://www.garethjmsaunders.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/forest-path.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-14604" srcset="https://www.garethjmsaunders.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/forest-path.jpg 750w, https://www.garethjmsaunders.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/forest-path-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Photo by Adrien Tutin on Unsplash</figcaption></figure>



<p>Life has been heavy recently, but it has also nudged me to choose a new direction. For a long time I have wanted to help people who feel overwhelmed and stretched in too many directions, but I never quite felt ready to share that publicly.</p>



<p>Yesterday I posted a small teaser on social media. Today I want to share the full story.</p>



<p>Over the years I have learned how to rebuild clarity, calm and a better way of working. These systems have helped me through some of the most challenging times of my life in the past twenty years, including raising children, working multiple jobs, divorce and redundancy. They brought me focus and steadiness when everything else was uncertain.</p>



<p>Now I am opening up <strong>1:1 Productivity and Agile Coaching</strong> for people who want that same clarity and calm.</p>



